  "id": "31b599843f24cc35056dd139",
  "title": "Waitakere Ranges Regional Park: Tasman Lookout",
  "summary": "今天这个地方可以说是Waitakere的最后一站了。 雾气腾腾的早上。 根据公园小册子，今天的计划是先去Tas […]",
  "content": "<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_11_9f6f276a-33e3-4749-ac49-b099260a67c4.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>今天这个地方可以说是Waitakere的最后一站了。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_3_9f6f27e4-91b2-4efc-b093-18645bf7e808.jpg?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>雾气腾腾的早上。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_14_9f6f27ce-b76e-4de4-8912-3221a5ab45c5.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>根据公园小册子，今天的计划是先去Tasman Lookout然后去爬Lion Rock。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_7_9f6f26fa-626a-42e9-a886-ca45b319f1b4.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Piha沙滩左侧是Tasman Lookout。找了半天没找到。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_4_9f6f2747-3d86-4e40-88e9-ac066868b863.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Waitakere给我的印象还是像以前一样，风景一流，开发落后。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_12_9f6f278d-9718-4385-af11-88bfa70aa576.jpg?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>徒手爬了一点石头山，拍了一点照片。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_6_9f6f2758-875a-4867-aacb-d9778aec4ff5.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>太高了不敢上，怕下不来。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_9_9f6f272c-5a54-41e5-843e-151b867b8bde.jpg?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>路上经过这个洞倒是蛮好玩的。石头山中间有个洞，海浪会冲刷进来。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_10_9f6f2742-53a8-478b-ad37-59aabba159de.jpg?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>跑到Piha右边去爬Lion Rock。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_15_9f6f27ea-adab-4170-833c-f65d570645a6.jpg?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>远远能看到那个年久失修的楼梯。并且被一条小溪拦住了去路。就放弃了。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_2_9f6f26fa-3dd8-49be-9552-c2fc05c830f2.jpg?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>这里的风景真的很好，很推荐来看看。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_5_9f6f274e-ab65-497b-a0be-1cd6bf25cc11.jpg?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>喜闻乐见的沙子纹理系列。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_1_9f6f2808-6613-408b-be38-ea73e944e5de.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>沙子真的很多变。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_8_9f6f2714-a403-4240-bf6a-739d32afa3a6.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>风和水都会把他们塑造成不同形状。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_16_9f6f27f4-f3f0-4968-b11f-defe91586ee9.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>还有沙子里面的生物，留下的气泡。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_13_9f6f27af-f8a7-47e4-beac-12126668f732.jpg?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>",
  "image": "https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_11_9f6f276a-33e3-4749-ac49-b099260a67c4.jpg",
  "publishedAt": "2025-07-22T21:48:52Z",
